//Create the tempalte in sitecore/content/template
1.We create the template TextBlock.
2.Name the secton name like TextBlockData.
3.Add Fields:
 a)Heading       Singletext type
 b)SubHeading    Singletext type
 c)Content       Richtext   type
 
4.Save it and publish!(Prefer smart publish)
 
//Create an sitecore/content/home 
1.Create an item using texblock template in Sitecore contentery.
2.Name the item as TextBlock.
3.Item fields willbe created and Fill text like below

a)Heading  --This is the Heading!
b)SubHeading--This is the Sub Heading!
c)Content--  Here is the Content!  
4.Save it and publish.(Prefer smart publish)



 
